      "description": "The Defiance Daily Target 2X Long Copper Miners ETF (COPZ) is an exchange-traded fund that mostly invests in materials equity. The fund seeks to deliver 2x leveraged exposure to the daily share price movement of the Global X Copper Miners ETF (COPX), net fees and expenses, through derivatives like swap agreements. COPZ was launched on Feb 17, 2026 and is issued by Defiance.",
